  - FX rate changes (Light, GBP/USD +5%): 8.46%, 1.35%, 90%, Impact 20; Moderate (+15%): 2.34%, 0.12%, 40%, Impact 40; Severe (+25%): –15.2%, –18.2%, 20%, Impact 90
